title: Slideshow: Scenes from Homecoming 2015 (University of Wisconsin-Madison)
text: ( Source : University of Wisconsin-Madison ) Oct. 17 , 2015 UW-Madison students, alumni and fans celebrated Homecoming 2015, highlighted by the traditional parade down State Street on Friday night. It was one of many Homecoming week activities
